    <content>&lt;h3 style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;Instructions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;The list below highlights the 11 strategies that were noted in the Pre-Course Self-Assessment. For a recap of definitions see &lt;a href="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Descriptions_11_Principles.pdf"&gt;Descriptions of 11 Strategies&lt;/a&gt;. Be sure to read about any strategies for which you scored yourself a 1 or 2 in the self-assessment. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
